Driver Drowsiness Detection 

This project detects whether a driver is feeling sleepy using AI.

Features

- Detects eye closure
- Gives alert when driver is drowsy

Tech Used

- Node.js
- Computer Vision
- Machine Learning

How to Run

1. Terminal 1:and run : npm run dev:servers

2. Terminal 2:and run : npm run dev:clients

